00228     PmReturn_t retval;
00229     uint8_t const *paddr = test_code_image0;
00230     uint8_t const *pimg = test_code_image0;

00240     /* Size occurs one byte after the type */

00245     CuAssertTrue(tc, pimg == (test_code_image0 + size));
00246
